### 1. 챌린지 참여 요청 생성
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/challenges/participations/1
Authorization: {{accessToken}}

### 2. 내가 참여한 챌린지 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/challenges/participations/my?status=PENDING&page=0&size=10
Authorization: {{accessToken}}

### 3. 챌린지 참여 요청 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/challenges/participations/1?status=PENDING&page=0&size=10
Authorization: {{accessToken}}

### 4. 챌린지 참여 요청 처리
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/challenges/participations/confirm/1?status=ACCEPTED
Authorization: {{accessToken}}

### 5. 챌린지 나가기
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/challenges/participations/leave/1
Authorization: {{accessToken}}